  01 Aug 2013; Sergey Popov <pinkbyte@gentoo.org> -blitz-0.9.ebuild,
  -blitz-0.9-r3.ebuild, -files/blitz-0.9-gcc-4.3-missing-includes.patch:
  Drop old versions, wrt bug #478574

*blitz-0.10-r1 (01 Aug 2013)

  01 Aug 2013; Sergey Popov <pinkbyte@gentoo.org> +blitz-0.10-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bump: EAPI 5, respect LDFLAGS, some cosmetic changes, drop unused
  inherit of multilib eclass

  13 Nov 2012; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> blitz-0.10.ebuild:
  Split doc building and compiling, resolving bug #442504

  19 Oct 2012; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> blitz-0.9.ebuild,
  blitz-0.9-r3.ebuild, blitz-0.10.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Remove virtual/fortran and always call fortran-2_pkg_setup as intend by the
  updated fortran-2.eclass

  20 Aug 2012; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org>
  +files/blitz-0.10-set-default-arg-value.patch, blitz-0.10.ebuild:
  Fix for unset variable when user specifically disable a default enabled
  feature. This also fixes bug #431594

  13 Aug 2012; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata.xml boost use flag description

